  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Prevocational Education for 35 Deaf students</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many Deaf students have limited educational opportunities with no support services in Guatemala. LAVOSI will provide basic instruction in sewing, textile production, culinary and gardening, and construction. Deaf students will learn the basics for life skills, independence and for seeking and creating job opportunities in careers that are commonly found in Guatemala. The inability to communicate closes doors to education and to the world of work. Prevocational learning is essential to survival.</narrative>
  </description>
